{"tid":723174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 游蕙禎出獄後首開腔稱搵工要緊 望「帶住過去經驗繼續行」","createTime":"2018-06-30T07:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T19:00:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"53ea21525575dc36682aab0061c26f5a086e0b8f","tid":723174,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"吃過午餐後，中午12時50分左右，游蕙禎離開酒店，只見她薄施脂粉，白色上衣配黑色短裙，精神奕奕。她首度開腔談及坐監感受，與及未來計劃。記者問她有否重生的感覺，她說：「唔可以叫『重生』，唯有帶住過去既經驗繼續行。」<br />\n<br />\n4星期的牢獄生涯，令游蕙禎感受深刻。她說：「裡面(監獄)感覺好靜好有規律，同外面感覺好唔同，畀我可以諗到多啲嘢。」她坦言，目前以生計為首要任務，「出嚟首先係要穩定番收入，搵番份工，任何人都需要生活。」至於明天會否參與7.1遊行，是否繼續從政？她未有具體答覆：「好多私人嘢要處理咗先，要睇吓...咁7.1都係一個表達途徑。」<br />\n本來已經纖瘦的游蕙禎，似乎再瘦一圈。較早前戰友為她買來至愛的炸雞做午餐，不過她表示其實沒有特別的食物想吃，又指會休息一會，「好攰，晏啲會探父母。」隨即登上私家車離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180630/58382928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F58382928&d=q37Okwz3dMy7n%2BC1cFV2dwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=893f7575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F58382928&h=5671416f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180630/58382928</a>"},{"pid":"90836579e909b6d0912276d85ec7ed3a8cabfe72","tid":723174,"uid":19454,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/152354_cd4c13d1f89570e235a984123aa9f70d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F152354_cd4c13d1f89570e235a984123aa9f70d.png&h=83920ea4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06489f645de291857faec193ab404be2bddd1c61","tid":723174,"uid":7961,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"始終都係搵工要緊"},{"pid":"3dc4a79505e8c67cf4b900367ec1bbecb56351b6","tid":